title: Generals honored at 2015 HTL Banquet
text:
Generals honored at 2015 HTL Banquet 
The 2015 Home Talent League awards banquet was held on Sunday at Rex’s Innkeeper in Waunakee. Several Fort Atkinson Generals were honored for their outstanding year, one that saw Fort advance to the Final Four before coming up one game short of playing for the league title. Pictured are Generals board members, from left, Jerry Brokl and Sandy Brokl, Dan Allard, Tim and Michelle Garant, and Jim Roethel. The Generals received plaques for winning both the Southeast Section title in Sunday League and East Section in Night League. The 2015 Brett Magritz Memorial Award recipient went to catcher Bryan Wallace of the Fort Generals. — Daily Union photos by Jeff Seisser.
